dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ultimately, it was less than 0.20 seconds that separated Hudson-Smith from gold, despite the Brit running a personal best on the Stade de France track.\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 493, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Team GB runner posted the fifth fastest time in history.\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 555, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, it was little consequence to Hudson-Smith, who could smell the gold medal with less than 10m to go.\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 29-year-old struggled to hold back his emotions after crossing the finish line, with Hudson-Smith shouting \\\"f**k\\\".\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Shortly after the waterworks followed, with Hudson-Smith consoled by a member of his party while looking visibly emotional.\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 909, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While it was tough ending, it was still an achievement to be proud of for Hudson-Smith.\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 998, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking to theBBCafter the race, he said: \\\"Yeah it's crazy.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1059, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Honestly, sometimes the journey is better than the outcome and it's been a hell of a journey.\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1153, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more:Team GB star could not hold back tears after missing out on Olympic medal    \\\"Came away with an Olympic silver, how many people in the world can say that.\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1319, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been the bridesmaid twice now, my time is coming.\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just happy.\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I saw my family, I did not even know they were here.\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a bit of a s